LAGOS  – ConnectNigria has announced that its monthly business meeting tagged ConnectNigeria Business Mixer will hold this Friday in Lagos. Uzor Anekwe, Business Development Manager at ConnectNigeria, said the objective of the meeting is to bring C-level executives, entrepreneurs, and pretty much everyone in need of business growth together to meet minds and discuss strategies for the year. He said, “With the second quarter of 2022 fast approaching, it is expected for business professionals to intensify efforts towards reaching their revenue goals and one of the most effective strategies is to attend networking events where you can meet decision-makers from organizations of interest.” Anekwe added that the Business Mixer by ConnectNigeria is the most recommended networking event for this business season, adding that, “Networking with decision-makers at the Business Mixer is easy because everyone in attendance is in the mood to meet new people, have fun and discuss business opportunities, in a relaxed environment.”